name: Timofey Borzov
title: Managing Director
headline: Managing Director at VTB
organization_short_description:
VTB Group is a global provider of financial services. The Group's companies offer a complete range of financial services including retail, corporate and investment banking; broking and other stock-market services; insurance; asset management for pension and unit funds; leasing; and more.

VTB Group operates large international network, offering a comprehensive range of services to clients in more than 20 countries across the CIS, Europe, Asia and Africa.

Together, VTB Bank and its subsidiaries (more than 50% owned) are known as VTB Group.
The Russian government owns 60.9% of VTB Bank's equity.

name: Alexey Severin
title: Managing Director
headline: Managing Director
organization_short_description:
Сбер — крупнейший банк в России, поставщик надёжных технологических решений и один из ведущих финансовых институтов страны. Мы не боимся меняться и открывать новые горизонты, но в то же время остаёмся верными принципам, сформированным за нашу 180-летнюю историю. Такой подход позволяет нам создавать и развивать десятки технологичных направлений. Нашими сервисами пользуются миллионы людей, а над их созданием и совершенствованием работают десятки тысяч сотрудников. 

Sber is the largest bank in Russia, supplier of reliable technological solutions and one of the leading national financial institutions. We are not afraid to change and open up new horizons, but at the same time we remain true to the principles that have been formed over our 180-year history. This approach allows us to create and develop dozens of technological areas. Our services are used by millions of people, and thousands of employees are working on their creation and improvement.

name: Marwan Ghalayini
title: Managing Director
headline: Director
organization_short_description:
AlShawaf international company is a story of success that extends for around thirty
years in Riyadh. We have always been impressed with a glamorous sense of sharing
our story and journey of excellence with our Saudi community. keeping this in mind,
our services were relatively small though at that time commenced in the heart and
mind of Dr. Abdulmoeen AlShawaf to serve the Saudi business community. Now,
these have expanded and grown big into various fields of services ranging from
bookselling and publishing to advertising, financial communications, digital screens,
art production, construction materials, and automotive heavy machinery.
We disseminated in several countries with several departments and subsidiaries,
including the kingdom of Saudi Arabia, United Arab Emirates, Turkey, and China.
We became pioneers and have gained a unique leading position in our business
field. Our first steps, in fact, were initiated in 1986, when we started the wholesale
and retail sale of merchandise, promotional items and later opening a bookstore
followed then by other business lines, Our professional management and team of
highly qualified personnel are diligent and have dedicated their efforts to meeting
not only the needs of our customers but also attaining their satisfaction. we look at
them as a top priority that should always be triggered and enhanced.

name: Awdesh Chetal
title: CEO and Cofounder
headline: Technology Entrepreneur, Startup Incubation, Venture Studio and Investor
organization_short_description:
HyperThink is a leading IT and business services company with a diverse services portfolio and a focus to provide integrated services in Technology and Operations. We provides IT consulting services, systems integration, packaged application services, elearning services and business process outsourcing services. We understand the broader business needs and environment of our clients and leverage our combined knowledge of business, technology, processes and global delivery expertise to offer customized solutions for our customers.

We primarily work in 6 vertical markets – Oil and Gas, Manufacturing, Financial Services, Real Estate, Education and the Public Sector. HyperThink is committed to helping its customers build and maintain leadership positions in their individual markets. Our team carries a relentless dedication to customer satisfaction and we can adapt, deploy, manage and support a broad portfolio of advanced technologies and services. 

As a global services organization, we have pioneered the global delivery model to deliver services from multiple global locations thereby offering better return on investment for our services. With our experience in offering solutions from multiple global locations, we have built our services model into a quality management system and knowledge base that enables our customers to integrate with global services rapidly and at a lower risk, thereby meeting the specific needs of their businesses.

title: Managing Director
headline: Internationally Experienced Business Leader ● Specialized Engineering ● Hard & Soft Commodities ●
organization_short_description:
TESCO Engineering is the Pioneer of OEM independent, high quality Specialized Services for Fluid & Gas Sealing, Rotating Equipment & Turbomachinery in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. TESCO Engineering excels at analyzing, re-engineering and refurbishment of your plant's Fluid & Gas handling equipment to be more efficient & reliable based on the implementation of the latest technology upgrades & materials, field service methodologies and analysis of equipment performance.

Combining Skill and Experience with a Passion for solving equipment challenges in our State-of-the-art Workshop facilities in Jubail & Yanbu, our multi disciplined Specialist Reliability Teams,  with an accumulated experience in excess of 180 years, cover a wide range of Rotating Equipment & Turbomachinery,  including Mechanical Seals, Dry Gas Seals, Engineered & Specialty Seals, Maintenance, Refurbishment, and Overhaul (MRO) of Pumps, Compressors, Steam Turbines, Industrial Refrigeration Packages, Gearboxes, Fans, Blowers, and their Auxiliary Systems independent and regardless of OEM.

In-house Engineering & Design capabilities enable TESCO Engineering to upgrade, redesign, and manufacture components for critical equipment in critical applications, with a proven track record of solving critical problems in some of the most complex applications in the O&G, Petrochemical, Energy & Water, Mining, and heavy Industries in the GCC region.

name: Sara Hamam
title: Marketing Director
headline: Marketing Director at Les Mills IMEA
organization_name: Les Mills India, Middle East & Africa (LMIMEA)
organization_short_description:
Les Mills has been delivering life-changing fitness experiences for over 50 years. Now an international fitness brand, we mix music, motivation and movement for millions around the globe through our world-class fitness programs. Our mission is simple – to create a fitter planet. 

We blur the boundaries of physical and digital experiences to bring our club partners ultimate fitness solutions. Feel our love for live group fitness with the iconic barbell workout BODYPUMP. Pedal through utopia and dystopia all in the same workout with the immersive cycle experience of THE TRIP. Reserve your spot in the front row of martial arts inspired BODYCOMBAT or any of our 1000+ workouts available on LES MILLS+.

Creating a fitter planet means more than exercise. We're dedicated to carbon neutrality, measuring and offsetting carbon dioxide emissions for each of our global offices. Through our BORN TO MOVE program and partnership with UNICEF, we're united in our ambition to create a world where every child survives and thrives. 

We're in the business of strength and allowing teammates to play to theirs. Diversity, equity and inclusion are a mindset and a culture; a healthy work-life balance an essential, and encouragement to ‘exercise your passion' fundamental.


لقد قامت شركة ليزملز بتقديم تجارب لياقة بدنية مغيرة للحياة لأكثر من 50 عاماً. الآن هذه العلامة التجارية العالمية للياقة البدنية، تقوم بمزج الموسيقى والتحفيز والحركة للملايين حول العالم من خلال برامج اللياقة البدنية ذات المستوى العالمي. مهمتها بسيطة - إنشاء كوكب ـأكثر لياقة.  

بدأت قصة ليزملز في عام 1968 عندما بدأ ليزملز، وهو رياضي أولمبي، أول صالة ألعاب رياضية له في أوكلاند، نيوزيلندا، لقد كانت عملية بسيطة ، وتمارين أساسية للقوة وتمارين الكارديو لمجتمع صغير من الرياضيين. الآن، بعد مرور 50 عامًا، أصبح مركزاً للثورة العالمية - وجهة نابضة بالحياة حيث يخلق أفضل مواهب اللياقة البدنية في العالم طرقًا جديدة للحصول على لياقتهم، والجمع بين الموسيقى والحركة ثم نقلها إلى العالم. 

كان ابن ليز فيليب ملز هو من قاد التغيير. ع

name: Debbie Gobbett
title: Marketing Director
headline: Marketing Director
organization_short_description:
WHO WE ARE: Press Play Online was formed in 2014 when we saw how important video was for websites and social media marketing - back then social media was in it's infancy, so we were delighted to be at the start of an exciting boom that was to be video for web! Derek has been filming wildlife, adrenalin activities and weddings since 1996 and I started as his assistant photographer at weddings back in 1997, so we used what we knew in photography & video and applied it to the new platform of the world wide web.

WHAT WE DO: video Production! Since 2014 we have filmed and photographed a fabulous variety of businesses, big and small, telling their unique stories and creating reach for their brands. From high end Real Estate to wine farms and golf courses, commercial coaching videos to health & fitness companies, small charities to investment videos for kids clothing brands and everything in-between. 

WHY WE DO IT: We love getting the shot that no one else can! Aerial Photography and Film is getting that birds eye view of a property or golf course that goes beyond the naked eye. Also, we're pretty nosey and love seeing the interior decor of other people's homes (for our real estate photography and video) we do love a social  game of golf (for our golf course marketing videos) and we are natural story tellers and love a beautiful shot for our wedding photography & videos.

CONTACT US: If you would like some creative video or photo imagery for your website or social media, do give me a call on +44 7557 397723 I would love to chat about your visual ideas and work with you

"Video is a marketing tool you cannot afford to pass up" - Forbes

headline: Entrepreneur, Finance Coach & Expert CFA Instructor
organization_short_description:
Leaders Training Centre & Leaders Languages Centre have made a history in fulfilling your training needs. These are prestigious destinations for your training needs & has emerged as a trusted and reliable training partner of individuals & corporates for their training & development needs in Qatar. We aspire to provide unparalleled training services & become a life long learning partner for working professionals by employing industry expert faculty that uses a combination of practical industry knowledge combined with management skills. Our areas of focus are on higher education pathways, professional development programs & vocational industry based training programs.  
We have also collaborated with many large scale international & local organizations to deliver corporate trainings & courses and has since created a rapport with these brands making them our regular clients when it comes to training. We are Silver Accredited Centre from NEBOSH. 
We are located in the heart of Doha, having premium facility with big size classrooms which makes classroom environment as a convenient place to learn & teach. 
In Leaders, our myriad of courses range from Accountancy & Finance, health & Safety, Business Management and Languages.

Rove Group was established in the year 1997, with its growing portfolio in the entirety of the MENA region and India. name: Rajeev Narayan
title: Managing Director
headline: Managing Director at Integra Projects and Facility Management
organization_short_description:
Integra Projects & Facility Management W.L.L. is an ISO 9001:2015, ISO 14001:2015 and ISO 45001-2018 certified leading solution provider, supplier, and system integrator of Electrical, M.E.P., Advanced Electronics, and Automation system providing its service for Residential, Infrastructural, Commercial and Oil & Gas segments in Qatar. We represent a broad spectrum of international companies, including prestigious multinationals in the state of Qatar. We consider ourselves to be one of the best organisations in Qatar, offering these solutions, having executed numerous medium and large-scale projects across multiple domains with Private, Semi-government and wholly government-owned entities alike.

We boast a strong specialised, vendor certified resource pool present locally to provide the best Facility Management services tailored to our customer requirements. Our solutions are focused on improving the efficiency & life of the asset through a well-defined international approved approach that will bring enormous cost savings and peace of mind to our customers. We intend to provide exceptional operational, technical, and commercial management of the assets by proposing solutions that are future proof, energy-saving & environment friendly with minimal risk and disruption of ongoing services.

Integra Projects & Facility Management W.L.L. is focused on providing customers with turnkey solutions from the conceptualisation of the project to maintaining the fully executed project throughout the life cycle of the project.

Our company employs over 150 employees with specialised functions to ensure the best quality service coupled with the best minimal lead time possible through a dynamic distributed approach with the value of service or solution retained with utmost sincerity. We maintain a considerable amount of Stock in our fully-fledged Workshop to ensure that our customers are not affected by delays due to delay in delivery.

name: Manhar Mohammed
title: Founder & Chief Executive Officer
headline: Founder & CEO @ Candidzone -  RPO | Strategic Recruitment | Staffing | Outsourcing-Manpower
organization_short_description:
We are a high-performance team of professionals who collectively make Candidzone-an Executive Search, Sourcing & Selection, Recruitment, Human Resources, and Employment Services, Talent Acquisition, Long-term Staffing, Interim Placements, Payroll Solutions, Training & Development, and Project Support Services providing organization.

Candidzone has been setting benchmarks in Qatar since 2012 across various industries, including Construction, Oil & Gas, Hospitality, Automotive, and Retail and many more. 

Our expertise includes Headhunting, Candidate Screening, and Job Placement, focusing not only on providing needed resources but also on creating trust-based long-term relationships with our clients. 

Our core competency lies in Workforce Management, Talent Management, and Professional Networking, collaborating with your organization and partnering with your team to implement Temporary Employment, Contract Staffing, and Staff Augmentation solutions. Our ever-expanding database, client reach, and broad network of contacts, enable us to take a systematic approach to connect the right solutions, right people, to the right services, and the right opportunities.

Candidzone has many advantages of local presence, including round-the-clock availability, industry-experienced consultants, expertise in Local Laws and Regulations, and Workplace Diversity awareness.

Ready to build your high-performing team? Contact Candidzone today for a free consultation and discover how we can help you achieve your workforce goals.

name: Alexander Konkov
title: Managing Director
headline: Managing Director
organization_short_description:
"Sistema"​ is the largest diversified publicly-traded investment company in Russia and the CIS, which invests in and is a major shareholder of companies serving over 100 million customers in the sectors of telecommunications, high technology, oil and energy, radars and aerospace, banking, retail, mass-media, tourism and healthcare services. Founded in 1993, the company reported revenues of US$ 7.9 billion for the first quarter of 2012, and total assets of US$ 47.3 billion as at March 31, 2012. Sistema's global depository receipts are listed under the symbol "SSA"​ on the London Stock Exchange. Sistema's ordinary shares are listed under the symbol "AFKS"​ on the MICEX-RTS Stock Exchange, and under the symbol "SIST"​ on the Moscow Stock Exchange (MSE). Sistema was ranked number 342 in the 2010 edition of the Fortune Global 500 list. 

Assets Portfolio - 
MTS (Telecommunications)
Bashneft (Oil Production and Refining)
Bashkirenergo (Energy Production and Distribution)

Detsky Mir (Retail)

Intourist (Tourism)
MEDSI (Healthcare)
RTI (Defence Solutions, Comprehensive Security Systems, Telecom Solutions, Microelectronics Solutions and System Integration)
Binnopharm (Biotechnologies and Pharma Productions)
NIS-GLONASS (Navigation Systems and Services)

name: Rajesh Khandare
title: Sales Director
headline: Sales Director
organization_short_description:
CRYO Services is a leading service provider for all your cryogenic needs in the United Arab Emirates. Our expertise are well renowned in the medical, industrial, food and specialty gas sectors.

At CRYO Services, our focus is always on delivering the best tailor made solution to our customers. Through the distribution of liquid gases, in small or bulk amounts, we pride ourselves in delivering reliability and efficiency to small and medium sized businesses around the Gulf. Our expertise lie in the hands of our team of highly qualified engineers who provide a full rounded solution from advising to installation. Primarily, consultation is provided on low and high pressure gas systems, supply of storage vessels, gas control equipment, pipeline installation and preventive maintenance in various industries including food and beverage, entertainment, hospitality, healthcare, beauty, oil and gas.

Cryo Services is on a mission to provide you with a one stop shop for all your installation and servicing needs of cryogenic equipment.

headline: Co-founder & CEO
organization_short_description:
AGORA - B2B платформа  электронной коммерции
 Мощная B2B платформа SAAS или на оборудовании заказчика с более чем 200 модулями

Достижения
Резидент Инновационного центра «Сколково».
Входим в состав Ассоциации ISDEF (Форум Независимых Разработчиков Программного Обеспечения).
Участник программы поддержки инновационных проектов Microsoft Startap Accelerator
ТОП 3 самых перспективных стартапов России в рейтинге "Russian Beyond The Headlines"  2012,2013
Входим в группу "100 инноваторов России" по версии Открытых инноваций
Лауреат "Стартап года 2013" и "Зворкинский проект"
 
Команда
Сегодня в составе команды 38+ высококлассных специалистов. Каждый из нас имеет достаточно опыта и навыков, но самая главная ценность - это желание каждого добиться общей цели. Дружный коллектив и замечательная атмосфера позволяет нам не "ходить на работу", а заниматься каждый день любимым делом.

Цель
Мы стремимся создать на российском рынке максимально удобные условия для развития B2B электронной коммерции. Узким горлышком зачастую является отсутствие автоматизации рутинных процессов между компаниями. Мы создаем и внедряем доступные решения как для лидеров рынка, так и для небольших оптовых фирм.

name: Waleed Talat
title: Co-Founder and CEO
headline: Founder, CEO, and Board Member at Arib
organization_short_description:
Arib is a Saudi fintech startup that operates in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. Having obtained a license from the Saudi Central Bank (SAMA), Arib aggregates financing options from various institutions on a single platform. This allows users to compare and select the most suitable financing option for their needs.
Arib was initially launched in late 2018 under the name syaaraat.com, focusing on digital brokerage for auto-leasing. While syaaraat.com is still operational, Arib has since expanded its services to include brokerage for other financial products, such as personal loans, mortgages, Credit Cards, and SMEs.
Through its aggregated marketplace, Arib aims to simplify the process of finding and securing the right financing options for its customers across this broader suite of financial services.

name: Mohammed Alnawkhani
title: Managing Director
headline: Managing Director
organization_short_description:
The Middle East Propulsion Company (MEPC) was formed in 1992 as a joint venture partnership and is an Economic Offset Company which exists under the Economic Offset Program (EOP) of Saudi Arabia. EOP is an innovative investment program established in 1989 to help form profitable businesses in Saudi Arabia. Designed to attract foreign investment, the program encourages joint ventures between foreign and Saudi companies which promotes the expansion of the Saudi private sector through long term, mutually beneficial, collaborative business ventures. MEPC provides military engine depot-level maintenance for Royal Saudi Air Force (RSAF) aircraft and remains committed to being a world class provider for overhaul of engines, parts, and services.

MEPC established and has maintained a good working relationship with the Royal Saudi Air Force (RSAF) since 2001 providing Maintenance, Repair, and Overhaul (MRO) services for the F100-PW-220 engine that powers the RSAF F-15 aircraft. Since that time, MEPC has produced over 680 F100 modules and has begun providing MRO services on the RSAF RB199 engine utilized on the Tornado aircraft. The very first RB199 Intermediate Turbine module was delivered in 2009. Additionally, MEPC has initiated development of MRO capabilities on the RSAF T-56 and PT6A-62 engine fleet.

MEPC has provided MRO services out of the new facility which is built in Riyadh near King Khaled International Airport Industrial Area.

name: Ibrahim Jaidah
title: C.E.O (owner)
headline: Managing Director at Arab Engineering Bureau
organization_short_description:
Arab Engineering Bureau (AEB) is an award-winning firm of architects, urban and master planners, interior, landscape and structural designers, engineers, quantity surveyors and project and design managers with a truly inimitable portfolio.

Founded in 1966 as the first architectural and engineering consulting firm in Qatar, AEB brings 56 years of experience to the construction industry. 

Beginning with just six employees in 1991, when the firm was acquired by its current CEO Ibrahim M. Jaidah, AEB's diversified human resource has grown to a current figure of over 450 highly qualified professionals of 33 different nationalities.

Over the past 56 years, the firm has evolved into a leading multi-disciplinary architectural design consultancy. AEB operates across the Middle East, with offices in Doha, Lusail and Muscat; and South East Asia, with our Manilla office. Building on the firm's pioneering work and consolidating a long-term commitment to future development in the region, AEB established an office in Muscat, Oman, under the brand of Ibrahim Jaidah Architects and Engineers. In 2023, another office was established in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia. 

AEB works across extensively divergent project scales, typologies and environmental conditions. In recent years, the firm has completed numerous commercial, residential, civic, institutional, educational and historic preservation projects for a variety of public and private clients in 15 countries.

organization_short_description:
NH Design Interiors was founded with a simple mission, to deliver the best of bespoke interior design. 

Since our inception in 2021, we have worked with clients from around the world to bring their property dreams to life. Whether you are looking to create the perfect family living space or turn your home into a long term investment project. Our role is to make it easy for you. It's simple, "Your Home, Our Priority."

We believe that our clients deserve the highest of quality through both excellence of service and exquisite products and design. By tailoring our approach on a one-to-one basis, we specialise in providing consultative and personalised design services that can reflect modern, industrial or classical design styles for Residential apartments and villas along with exterior landscaping solutions.

name: Ali Mustafawi
title: Managing Director
headline: MD at Qatar Building Company
organization_short_description:
Qatar Building Company was founded in 1971 as a general civil engineering and building contractor. It has since established itself as a national market leader and has, over the years, incorporated material production and sales divisions into its structure to ensure self-reliance and a guarantee of quality. It takes a serious interest in promoting safety and protection of the environment, and its broad client base (from government agencies, international contractors and gas majors to private developers) illustrates the confidence the company generates. The Company owners have an experienced management team of people whose qualifications cover both commercial and engineering disciplines. Together the team brings a wealth of industry experience accumulated over decades to the Company.

Qatar Building Company is listed Grade ‘A' in all disciplines of the Government Central Tenders Committee, and is therefore qualified to undertake projects at all levels of cost and complexity.

headline: Sales Director at Ambitek UAE
organization_short_description:
Founded in 2010 in the UK / Founded in 2023 in the UAE.

Ambitek specialise in providing permanent & contract solutions.

We have a successful track record of placing candidates with skills and experience within Assembly & Maintenance, Design & Drawing Office, Foundry & Metallurgy, Machining & Tooling, Quality & Inspection, Welding & Fabrication, Site Based Engineering, Skilled Trades, Professional & White-Collar Engineering, Production & Logistics and Controls & Instrumentation.

We can successfully source skilled personnel to work in a wide range of industries including Aerospace, Automation, Automotive, Biotech, Chemical, Civil Engineering, Construction, Energy, Marine, Pharmaceutical, Oil & Gas, Rail & Utilities.

We recruit on behalf of a wide range of clients including established SME's to FTSE 100 & Fortune 500 organisations.

name: Abdullah Alnameh
title: Managing Director
headline: Managing Director at Qatar Charity
organization_short_description: Qatar Charity is a Doha-based non-governmental organization founded in 1992 in accordance with the laws and regulations governing charitable work in the State of Qatar. The Qatari society was expressing a deep willingness to contribute to the international solidarity chain and to participate in addressing the most important development and humanitarian challenges faced by vulnerable communities around the world. This willingness was derived from the Qatari society's values, principles and cultural heritage and Qatar Charity came as the institutional solution that would cater to it. Initially founded to provide life-saving assistance to children affected by conflicts or natural disasters, Qatar Charity then expanded its areas of expertise to include various humanitarian and development aid fields in which it has spent more than $1.3bn between 2013 and 2017, providing relief and assistance to more than 110 million beneficiaries worldwide.

organization_short_description: Since 1994, DataServ has delivered Accounts Payable invoice automation solutions that enable accounting teams to eliminate data entry, increase accuracy, and focus on higher-value tasks. As pioneers of the finance SaaS market, DataServ solutions are simply incomparable. Our solutions integrate seamlessly, but can also be used independently, giving us the unique capability to offer our clients the ability to evolve into the full solution at their own pace. Our document intake solution is second to none, with over 99% clean data output in 24 hours. Only DataServ can offer you true touchless invoice processing with our proprietary AutoVouch system.

name: Sergey Fedotov
title: Managing Director
headline: Managing Director at VTB
organization_short_description:
VTB Group is a global provider of financial services. The Group's companies offer a complete range of financial services including retail, corporate and investment banking; broking and other stock-market services; insurance; asset management for pension and unit funds; leasing; and more.

VTB Group operates large international network, offering a comprehensive range of services to clients in more than 20 countries across the CIS, Europe, Asia and Africa.

Together, VTB Bank and its subsidiaries (more than 50% owned) are known as VTB Group.
The Russian government owns 60.9% of VTB Bank's equity.
